      "content": "thanks. i like the vibe. i want to add a bit of conflict to the scene though to make it more dramatic. usually in these kinds of settings, there's a lot of tension between the older generation and the kids, right? like, maybe the parents are worried about certain things guys in that community are getting into or just how they're being perceived by the world? how would that tension play out at the table?",
